{"tid":2440985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★《彭博》瑞士交易商2.8億買銅　到中國竟變一堆石頭","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T12:00:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1057561fd4f0d7110a328d91f96794e22fd0e52e","tid":2440985,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"《彭博》報道，瑞士大宗商品貿易商Mercuria Energy Trading去年向一間土耳其供應商Bietsan Bakir達成協議，採購價值3,600萬美元（約2.8億港元）的粗銅，但當貨物到達中國後先發現，箱內的粗銅早已被掉包成彩繪岩石。<br />\n<br />\nMercuria稱自己是詐騙案的受害者，去年購買近一萬噸的粗銅，在從伊斯坦布爾附近的港口將近6,700噸的粗銅已分裝到8艘船的300多個貨櫃箱，經過查驗後貼好封條，但詐欺集團趁着夜幕打開貨櫃箱，將銅迅速掉包成鋪路石，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>這些石頭被噴上類似銅金屬的顏色，然後再貼上假封條來混淆。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n該公司聘用的律師Sinan Borovali表示，每隔幾日，當船隻離開Ambarli的港口碼頭時，就會發生同樣的事情，銅在夜晚被暗中卸下，取而代之的是塗有油漆的岩石。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/597486/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%95%862-8%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E9%8A%85-%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%9F%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%86%E7%9F%B3%E9%A0%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F597486%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%2595%25862-8%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%258A%2585-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A0%2586%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplVuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=52117e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/597486/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%95%862-8%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E9%8A%85-%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%9F%E8%AE%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%86%E7%9F%B3%E9%A0%AD</a>"},{"pid":"4ac1b32533a27a06577dbc681ddd4060b5e53b57","tid":2440985,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji